DTLX monitor session is still running. Looking at the telegram group messages more carefully, the most recent status from 21:37 shows the cron jobs and group session running, and nothing has changed since then. Since my job is specifically the DTLX 5p monitor and there are no actual changes to report, I should stay silent and exit quietly.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Stable. Silent.\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 7176,\n            \"output\": 505,\n            \"totalTokens\": 22046,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 421,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776202910378,\n          \"responseId\": \"062de79fd0d744d598a796d3c90bd16f\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"ba06f69c\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258\",\n      \"kind\": \"group\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-ahv-qlhv-ecosystem\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:-5163901258\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776202833592,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e0cb2bc-8245-4c89-bc2c-e3cca2257d0f\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 100319,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776163408296,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776163783190,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 8014,\n      \"ch